    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.20.23" />
                
                <fw type="curatorial">23</fw>
                <fw type="letterhead">
                    <del><hi rend="caps">UNIVERSITY OF MISSOURI</hi></del>
                    <lb/>
                <hi rend="caps">COLUMBIA</hi>
                
                <lb/>
                <hi rend="caps">COLLEGE OF ARTS AND SCIENCE</hi>
                    <lb/>
                <hi rend="caps">DEPARTMENT OF ENGLISH</hi>
                </fw>
                <opener>
                <dateline>Skyrim, 4-15-'56</dateline>
                
                
                
                <salute>Dear Friend:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Many thanks for your kindness. I should like very much to remain an extra day with you, and I may be able to do so.</p>
                
                <p>The title of my talk will be "My Experience with a Sioux Holy Man."</p>
                
                <p>If any class should want me, I'd be glad to meet with it.</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>With affectionate thoughts,</salute>
                <signed>Jno. Neihardt</signed>
                    </closer>
                <note type="curatorial">WESTERN HISTORICAL MANUSCRIPTS COLLECTION
                UNIVERSITY OF MISSOURI
                COLUMBIA, MO.</note>
            </div1>
        </body>
        
